info.description:
# nucliadb

This package is an aggregation of all the other packages for a monolithic process


# CHANGELOG

## 2.0.16

- Fix bug in train service returning entity positions

## 2.0.15

- Fix bug on text highlighting

## 2.0.14

- Revert returning classification labels on resource list.

## 2.0.13

- Include processing queue type info on resource

## 2.0.12

- Return classification labels on search results and resource list

## 2.0.11

- Fix RuntimeErrors on client disconnect

## 2.0.10

- Fix local shard delete resource

## 2.0.9

- Be resilient if proxy cannot provide an account_seq

## 2.0.8

- Consume account_seq from push instead from pull

## 2.0.7

- Be able to reindex a resource and its vectors

## 2.0.6

- Extend BrokerMessage to include account queue sequence
- Include last account sequence on resource results

## 2.0.5

- Fix transactional error with TiKV when trying to get a nonexistent
  KB by slug

## 2.0.4

- Extend OpenAPI autogenerated docs and improve endpoints
  documentation

## 2.0.3

- Remove strong pinning

## 2.0.2

- Merge all subpackaged inside nucliadb
- Initial release
